Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Total duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Closed' in cases where 'Completed + In Call' occurs before 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved' in the fastest resolved cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases with more than one occurrence of this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases leading to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the next activity for all variants where 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' is followed by 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the variant with the highest performance
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the variant with the lowest performance
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases with 'Completed + In Call' against cases without

Name: Average elapsed time before 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' following 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total elapsed time of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the top 5 longest cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case
